	.container
		.row.mb-5
			.col-lg-12.text-center
				.squiggle
				h6 A Holistic Approach
				h2 My Creative Process
				p.lead This isn't just about a website; it's a collaborative journey. From our initial free consultation call to the final delivery of your website project, I'm committed to a streamlined and efficient process. Your input is not only welcomed but crucial to ensuring the end result aligns perfectly with your vision.
		.row
			.col-md-4.mb-5
				i.fad.fa-seedling
				h5 
					span 01. 
					| Discovery
				p I assist you in developing creative design concepts that align with your vision and conduct market research to establish an authentic online presence. During the Discovery phase, we discuss project objectives, target audience, and competitor analysis.
			.col-md-4.mb-5
				i.fad.fa-water
				h5
					span 02. 
					| Scope & Planning
				p I specialize in crafting engaging customer journeys that transform your website visitors into loyal customers. My process involves developing website sitemaps, flowcharts, and ideation sessions to ensure a seamless online experience.
			.col-md-4.mb-5
				i.fad.fa-pencil-paintbrush
				h5 
					span 03. 
					| Design Production
				p My expertise lies in creating user-centric design mockups that bring your brand identity to life. Using software tools such as Figma, I tailor each design to your company's specific requirements and integrate your branding to produce visuals that truly embody your unique style.
		.row
			.col-md-4.mb-5
				i.fad.fa-code
				h5 
					span 04. 
					| Development
				p I specialize in developing websites that are responsive, meeting modern technical standards and providing seamless experiences for both desktop and mobile users. I carefully evaluate your company's needs and select the most suitable technologies.
			.col-md-4.mb-5
				i.fad.fa-browser
				h5 
					span 05. 
					| Testing
				p To ensure your website's success, the final process involves thorough testing on all major browsers, operating systems, and devices.
			.col-md-4.mb-5
				i.fad.fa-hand-holding-seedling
				h5 
					span 06. 
					| Deployment + Handoff
				p Once your website is ready, I will deploy it and hand it off to you, ensuring a seamless transition. You'll experience a stunning website that not only represents your business, but also aligns with your strategic objectives. 
			
